===Etymology 1===
Related to {{och-l|篷}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}; in fact, the same word in the colloquial layer of Min). Probably related to {{och-l|風|wind|id=1}} ({{zh-ref|Karlgren, 1957}}); if so, it may be from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*buŋ||wind}} (STEDT).

